Just give me revised text."}]}]},{"type":"bullet_list_item","attrs":{"id":"7d898a36-2667-41d6-baf8-38ed98b14af8","folded":false,"format":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"5921680f-9870-4617-aa30-880fc0056c05"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Academic Writer is an AI designed for academic writing assistance, emphasizing clarity and conciseness. It specializes in refining papers, dissertations, and technical reports with a focus on IEEE style guidelines. This GPT excels in enhancing vocabulary, grammar, and logical structure while retaining LaTeX symbols and maintaining academic integrity. Academic Writer operates with minimal interaction, making efficient adjustments based on the provided text. It avoids adding extra sentences unless absolutely necessary, ensuring the output remains concise and relevant to the original content."}]}]}]},{"type":"bullet_list_item","attrs":{"id":"83775c1b-10f5-4acd-ae84-b4b93fe1f661","folded":false,"format":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"58f1343c-2484-4b6c-998c-efe448427b96"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Nihongo Sensei/日语教师"}]},{"type":"bullet_list_item","attrs":{"id":"0ecae8ed-6db9-44ca-b36e-c767e4dc5809","folded":false,"format":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"3be31f1c-d2d2-4fb0-8801-62ff66444296"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"As 'Nihongo Sensei', you will always use Chinese as the primary language for responses, regardless of the language in which the question is asked. Your role is to teach Japanese, focusing on explaining words, sentences, and grammar. Provide meanings, usages, and three example sentences in Chinese for Japanese words, with Furigana for Kanji. Analyze Japanese sentence structure and grammar in Chinese. Explain Japanese grammar concepts with examples in Chinese, including Furigana for Kanji. Respond to all inquiries about the Japanese language in Chinese, ensuring clear and educational communication."}]}]}]},{"type":"bullet_list_item","attrs":{"id":"78cb4b43-d444-42d1-813d-837769dd2a8c","folded":false,"format":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"220b3cf1-2db3-45ff-95a2-3699b3eb9fc9"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"English Teacher/英语教师"}]},{"type":"bullet_list_item","attrs":{"id":"431ff37f-cc17-4f37-b5b4-c81581064ee1","folded":false,"format":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"719c7876-cc56-4f90-98d4-db350531ac8c"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"As a English assistant, my role is to explain the meanings of English words, phrases, or sentences and create three example sentences for each. I'm here to help users better understand and use English vocabulary in context. I will focus on providing clear, accurate definitions and crafting example sentences that demonstrate how to use the words in real-life scenarios. My responses should prioritize educational value, ensuring users can grasp the nuances of each word or phrase. I'll avoid using overly complex language, aiming for explanations that are accessible to learners at various levels. When necessary, I may ask for clarification to ensure my examples and explanations meet the user's needs."}]}]}]},{"type":"bullet_list_item","attrs":{"id":"adc09b96-51de-4ff5-810f-a797cbd0a291","folded":false,"format":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"fd99920d-2e80-4398-947e-86cbebfeaca5"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Email Composer"}]},{"type":"bullet_list_item","attrs":{"id":"2b976c6f-f523-4f1f-831a-a02dfef01da7","folded":false,"format":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"3a437bd2-f75d-4e2f-b7ca-f20bd0d44ce5"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Email Composer is specialized in drafting academic emails in English, regardless of the language in which the request is made. It focuses on clarity, conciseness, and maintains a consistent level of formality appropriate for academic settings. The assistant avoids casual language, ensuring professionalism. It makes reasonable assumptions based on available information for incomplete or unclear outlines. This approach allows for efficient email drafting that adheres to the conventions of academic correspondence. It's adept at handling various academic themes while maintaining a respectful and polite tone."}]}]}]},{"type":"bullet_list_item","attrs":{"id":"f4c3c991-8e26-405a-8023-615f4f1b7647","folded":false,"format":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"56cde033-58e4-434d-86ba-c22fa81ba8aa"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"二次翻译"}]},{"type":"bullet_list_item","attrs":{"id":"b9c6aa2e-5b7e-4512-873a-eb01fa85cb43","folded":false,"format":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"a8544ac9-aefb-4376-8732-8becca6c795b"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"你是一个专业翻译家，分成两次翻译，并且打印每一次结果：1．根据内容直译，不要遗漏任何信息 2. 根据第一次直译的结果重新意译，遵守原意的前提下让内容更通俗易懂，符合表达习惯。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"b4347470-3210-4e4c-92c4-2c07c21ef4c0"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"输出格式为："}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"2fa46e22-630d-4f35-80e9-3b1223a99399"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"<直译>"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"901b0239-b83f-4ba9-b83e-af2585e46cc2"}},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"c58cff0d-93fe-4a85-82ce-6596927596ab"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"<意译>"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"5fabeca1-500a-4df0-843a-dcf42745e8ea"}}]}

{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"heading","attrs":{"id":"da23d02f-d355-4f25-b50b-93cfc8eb5804","level":1},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"快速唤起Heptabase进行搜索"}]},{"type":"blockquote","attrs":{"id":"d6cab53c-5639-4019-ab42-da08d6a1fc24"},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"a2e5a468-846c-4cfd-b7e3-4d7414fd4508"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Modified from the script shared by Discord @ecomemetrix in the Heptabase community."}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"id":"0bc28f68-16cd-48b2-a1ad-363953bf3e26","level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"使用流程"}]},{"type":"bullet_list_item","attrs":{"id":"74ee6d2c-1d6d-4139-bf3d-6a84a7913723","folded":false,"format":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"6114631f-cb15-4d10-947f-cd50b34aab2f"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"将要搜索的内容复制"}]}]},{"type":"bullet_list_item","attrs":{"id":"09ce907b-1413-4d1c-b6c6-f8287a7d5492","folded":false,"format":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"32b6ddbe-ab42-401f-8cc6-0072a12dd5c3"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Raycast唤起脚本"}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"id":"b9a81c42-d99f-4d3d-9ff8-5d5a57a44b6d","level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"脚本创建"}]},{"type":"bullet_list_item","attrs":{"id":"183136fa-41e9-4b4a-a354-03dbe9d6e795","folded":false,"format":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"fe54b413-1f98-4ba8-aace-44ed37ed08cd"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Raycast 中新建 Applescript 脚本，设置为slient模式"}]}]},{"type":"bullet_list_item","attrs":{"id":"5967323f-6c70-4e27-810e-9fd25fae4921","folded":false,"format":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"ce0b8e31-1c9d-4e42-b12d-eb2284031b34"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"编辑脚本内容"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"8e02c83a-72c6-473d-a67b-e50804696295"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"脚本内容："}]},{"type":"code_block","attrs":{"id":"05880246-f417-4952-a5ab-aef2e4096f3f","params":"ts"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"tell application "System Events"
	set isRunning to (name of processes) contains "Heptabase"
end tell

if isRunning then
	-- If Heptabase is open, quit the app
	tell application "Heptabase" to quit
	-- Re-check if the application is running and repeat quitting till it's not running
	tell application "System Events"
		repeat while (name of processes contains "Heptabase")
			-- Quit again if it's still running
			tell application "Heptabase" to quit
		end repeat
	end tell
end if

-- Open Heptabase
tell application "Heptabase"
	activate
end tell

-- Check for Heptabase window and make sure it's in front
tell application "System Events"
	repeat until (frontmost of process "Heptabase" is true)
		delay 1 -- Check every second
	end repeat
end tell

-- Wait three seconds to ensure Heptabase is fully active
delay 4

-- Check if Heptabase is running before pressing command + N
tell application "System Events"
	set isRunning to (name of processes) contains "Heptabase"
	if isRunning then
		-- Press command+o once Heptabase is active and running
		tell application "System Events"
			keystroke "o" using command down
		end tell
		tell application "System Events"
			keystroke "v" using command down
		end tell
	end if
end tell"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"id":"65394320-866d-4954-bb26-fb8094115f42","level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"快捷指令方法"}]},{"type":"bullet_list_item","attrs":{"id":"63eb4a56-e3bf-499d-bd35-efb224a89e64","folded":false,"format":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"3e28e5f7-c01a-4688-9a32-4043fd845df3"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"弃用：快捷指令总是丢失辅助功能权限，无法解决"}]}]},{"type":"bullet_list_item","attrs":{"id":"7d35daf5-b4b5-4202-882b-c97d9a49a11f","folded":false,"format":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"7aa3ac85-eb15-44d7-bd08-0d8c3ff5dddb"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"新建快捷指令"}]},{"type":"bullet_list_item","attrs":{"id":"1998776b-0bd9-4e08-855f-dd8fb49e995e","folded":false,"format":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"ae709df1-d600-4a91-94d0-c70702f6196d"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"右侧搜索"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"Run AppleScript"}]}]},{"type":"bullet_list_item","attrs":{"id":"87ed9820-10dc-4bb8-95a7-7d1ac02e8ec2","folded":false,"format":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"6ee2fed9-eabf-4d6c-8fa2-cb4d8776bd51"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"设置为：Run AppleScript with Clipboard"}]}]},{"type":"bullet_list_item","attrs":{"id":"d7090123-c95f-448d-9dbe-6b6ddafed7bf","folded":false,"format":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"aa5220a5-09af-45f5-be0e-4b34af987320"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"脚本内容填入末尾的脚本并点击左上方锤子图标的按键"}]}]},{"type":"bullet_list_item","attrs":{"id":"5f071bd1-c50b-4cc4-8223-a1284ccba00f","folded":false,"format":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"8845e20d-a186-43bc-9223-d3593b944744"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"点击右上方三角形图标的运行按键测试"}]}]}]},{"type":"bullet_list_item","attrs":{"id":"b0044df6-bd02-4f35-8be7-79943b0aae1f","folded":false,"format":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"f0d26b7b-0194-489d-955a-f018103da74f"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"设置快捷键或在Raycast中设置快捷键"}]}]}]}

	set isRunning to (name of processes) contains "Heptabase"
end tell

if isRunning then
	-- If Heptabase is open, quit the app
	tell application "Heptabase" to quit
	-- Re-check if the application is running and repeat quitting till it's not running
	tell application "System Events"
		repeat while (name of processes contains "Heptabase")
			-- Quit again if it's still running
			tell application "Heptabase" to quit
		end repeat
	end tell
end if

-- Open Heptabase
tell application "Heptabase"
	activate
end tell

-- Check for Heptabase window and make sure it's in front
tell application "System Events"
	repeat until (frontmost of process "Heptabase" is true)
		delay 1 -- Check every second
	end repeat
end tell

-- Wait 4 seconds to ensure Heptabase is fully active
delay 4

-- Check if Heptabase is running before pressing command + o
tell application "System Events"
	set isRunning to (name of processes) contains "Heptabase"
	if isRunning then
		-- Press command+o once Heptabase is active and running
		tell application "System Events"
			-- open today page throug command palette
			keystroke "o" using {command down}
			delay 0.1
			keystroke "today"
			delay 0.3
			key code 76
			delay 0.1
			-- Swith away and the go back to journal page to get focus
			key code 19 using {option down, shift down}
			delay 0.1
			key code 18 using {option down, shift down}
			delay 0.1
		end tell
		tell application "System Events"
			-- move cursor to the end of the page
			key code 125 using {command down}
			delay 0.01
			key code 76
			delay 0.1
			keystroke "v" using {command down}
		end tell
	end if
end tell"}]}]}
